{"tid":563443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉業強為香港求得中籤：家宅興旺，自身平安","createTime":"2018-02-17T02:53:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-17T04:02:03.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"170d07065fc3632f23affd0c40c0c1af9bd16b8b","tid":563443,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T02:53:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180217/s00001/4dc3b611ed302f004aace1c01d547311.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180217%2Fs00001%2F4dc3b611ed302f004aace1c01d547311.jpg&h=d7e30cf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新界鄉議局主席劉業強大年初二在車公廟為香港求得21籤中籤，籤文為「頃畝之田歲月深，祖宗創積到於今；勸君勿論多和少，寸土原來一寸金」。劉業強認為，籤文代表香港有很好的根基，只要香港向前行就會進步。<br />\n<br />\n該支中籤籤文解曰：「家宅興旺，自身平安；求財半遂，占病不妨」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，沙田鄉事委員會副主席李志麒則為沙田求得41中籤，籤文為「攝衣欲過灘頭淺，轉計回來怕濕身；人若不信辛苦事，何能取得保安寧」。"},{"pid":"c25a80478dcebb8edb09ec06b3b63275e12e6165","tid":563443,"uid":642,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T03:07:01.000Z","msg":"寸土原來一寸金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"111a5b1cbbfe14c8e11355dc60cf0adb4f75d4bb","tid":563443,"uid":68556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T03:17:46.000Z","msg":"樓價暢旺，咁要買多d樓。  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855534cc045e5d06f94ae46e58732e9a1ffd1924","tid":563443,"uid":161311,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T03:24:18.000Z","msg":"劉皇叔都死咗喇，阿斗你幫香港求籤？你邊位呀？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/17/112326_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F17%2F112326_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=50b16a6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a8ccf4b515daab9d8bfeba0ff04670762cb1387","tid":563443,"uid":21277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T03:28:09.000Z","msg"